What you need to know:

Kayange noted that Ayimba helped him develop his rugby profession back in 2006 when he appointed him Kenya Sevens captain, bypassing other experienced players in the team.“When I met him for the first time in early 2006, he dismissed me as slim, not able to cope with the game. That I needed more muscles,” said Kayange, who was shocked when Ayimba picked him captain towards the end of 2006.